.DS_Store
.envrc.local
# Machine-local mise overrides (issue #296): the template's sentinel tasks tell
# consumers to override scheme/destination-style config in .mise.local.toml,
# whose recommended header says "gitignored, never committed". Both spellings —
# mise honors mise.local.toml and .mise.local.toml. NOTE: gitignore never
# untracks an already-committed file, so the nested-python convention of a
# COMMITTED .mise.local.toml (dotfiles) keeps working; a NEW repo following
# that convention needs a one-time `git add -f`.
.mise.local.toml
mise.local.toml
*.log
node_modules/
dist/
build/
coverage/
reports/

